item.description:
description Script for adding Encoder from yaml file via jinja2
details adds an encoder to an axis, based on a yaml config file
author Anders Sandström
paramters FILE the yaml-file containing the PLC definition DEV the device name (optional, defaults to ${IOC}
Example calls:
call ${SCRIPTEXEC} &#34;./loadYamlEnc.cmd&#34; &#34;FILE=./enc.yaml&#34; ${SCRIPTEXEC} &#34;./loadYamlEnc.cmd&#34; &#34;FILE=./enc.yaml, DEV=foobar&#34;
